Record FieldMapping<T,​K>

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.hotels.transformer.model.FieldMapping<T,​K>
Type Parameters:
T - source element type
K - target element type
Record Components:
sourceFieldName - the field name in the source object
destFieldName - the field name in the destination object.
public record FieldMapping<T,​K>(T sourceFieldName, K destFieldName)
extends Record
Specifies the field's name mapping between the source object and destination one.
